# screenshots/

PNG captures for README showcases. Anything dropped here becomes available to
reference from README.md via `screenshots/<name>.png`.

Capture from niri (see .config/niri/config.kdl):
  Print             region (slurp selector)
  Mod+Print         whole screen
  Mod+Shift+Print   focused window

All captures land in `~/Pictures/Screenshots/` — rename and move into this
directory, then reference in README.md.

Suggested shots:
  desktop.png                 full workspace (Mod+Print)
  noctalia-launcher.png       Mod+Space opened, then Mod+Print
  noctalia-control.png        Mod+S opened, then Mod+Print
  nvim.png                    nvim + telescope/neo-tree (Mod+Shift+Print)
  terminal.png                kitty with fastfetch banner
